com.thomsonreuters.upa.rdm

Class Dictionary.VerbosityValues

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thomsonreuters.upa.rdm.Dictionary.VerbosityValues
  • Enclosing class:
    Dictionary

    public static class Dictionary.VerbosityValues
extends java.lang.Object
    Enumerations describing how much information about a particular dictionary is desired. These values are typically set in a RequestMsg's MsgKey filter when the request for the dictionary is made. See the UPA RDM Usage Guide for details.
    See Also:
    DataDictionary, MsgKey
